{"tid":1477733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山利安邨 青年偷拍狂 少女小心","createTime":"2019-08-16T08:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:23:00.000Z","uid":259933,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6653b5cf6603ed2b9183428a641353d9d97aac29","tid":1477733,"uid":259933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山利安邨 青年偷拍狂 少女小心<br />\n<br />\n懷疑被人偷拍<br />\n<br />\n如果知我係個 請麻煩<span style=\"color: green;\">唔好tag</span>我出黎 感謝TT<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZqaiPe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZqaiPe.jpg&h=d760d915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0V9N5vn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0V9N5vn.jpg&h=92bb6716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先 我覺得你非常之唔尊重 唔係女仔一著得性感少少 應該俾人係咁望 甚至係偷拍 係正常 再者 有冇諗過其實我同你對望過 我係會記得你個樣 如果再見到你 我應該會jer 9住你黎問 如果你識做 就唔該del咗張相去  雖則我知你唔會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有人識佢唔該send呢個post俾佢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n偷拍都唔識偷 仲要比我周到 俾我影番轉頭 你呢啲人唔可以放過 睇黎你係偷拍新手？有冇諗過 周圍都係監視器 如果想告你其實好易入 仲有 你電話就算剷除左張相 都可以攞部電話出去整 復原呢堆相 你嘅行為看似刺激 但其實好低能 唔好搞咁多啦<br />\n<br />\n如果各下女性俾人偷拍 唔好驚 要即刻攞部手機出嚟影佢 iPhone 開live photo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果你大嗌 香港人一定會沖出嚟幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地點:<span style=\"color: red;\">馬鞍山</span>利安邨<br />\n<br />\n日期:8月15<br />\n<br />\n時間:08:31am<br />\n<br />\n疑犯特徵: 身高目測180以上 25以上 正常人身形 唔肥唔瘦 眼細 內雙眼皮/單眼皮 戴眼鏡(佢副眼鏡框係深色) 圓面  正常人膚色  偏白少少 黑色/深色頭髮 髪形露額 短陰/gel佐頭（冇記錯唔係飛機頭）<br />\n<br />\n事發過程: <br />\n<br />\n我行緊去搭車 然後佢係我隔離行過 近距離眼神接觸左一下 跟住我望住佢右手 而是偷拍 懷疑係錄緊片 右手保持唔郁既話就肯定專登 呢個係咪更加肯定我覺得佢係偷拍<br />\n<br />\n題外話: 你知唔知低炒咁樣影我 我真係好撚肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d94e209899363dd04c83aefebaa6a7f6bbc0a9","tid":1477733,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"捉鳩住佢啦<br />\n仲影 ？普通市民有最低拘捕？"},{"pid":"6c0ebe0e38d659b18962874b97f3c5ce1984732b","tid":1477733,"uid":276162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0WQd7h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0WQd7h.gif&h=2f8b1f58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63c4d9e56c1cab9feeaa5bca2f9f0de8610ed158","tid":1477733,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"樓主係肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到條友出黎"},{"pid":"fcdce12800d53a7769d61225bfaa791273a79e97","tid":1477733,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:28:52.000Z","msg":"又多背包相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde3fcca11d2b45e24d2ef43ea348e3c653c2dc0","tid":1477733,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"連側面都見唔到 點同你認"},{"pid":"488185db3e53d99c686a5375090dd544f5eb3bba","tid":1477733,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:30:13.000Z","msg":"最撚憎偷拍狂<br />\n根本捉到要搞大佢"},{"pid":"ad5ad9996346cd1a23dcf2e239d3938924b96b1d","tid":1477733,"uid":183344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"樓主身型應該幾正"},{"pid":"ad7d989e80c855f3939de42a2270647e3cea019c","tid":1477733,"uid":183344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:31:49.000Z","msg":"樓主身型應該幾正"},{"pid":"fb52f0d9f1491415bd2beddd795c5365d7eb654d","tid":1477733,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"條友衣着都係斯文，咁都忍唔住要偷拍樓主，樓主一定好正着到好淫<br />\n利申想同樓主交配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec41eba2da934e819538aadb910600145a8aefeb","tid":1477733,"ui